# ==========================================
# NOTE: The following are intentionally NOT ignored
# so all project data is visible in the repo:
#   - backend/database/app.db         (SQLite database)
#   - backend/database/schema.sql     (Database schema)
#   - backend/database/*.db           (All databases)
#   - backend/scripts/*.py            (Data generation scripts)
# ==========================================
